hexs - just convert input byte stream to hex string

Examples:

% printf 'Example stream: \x7f\x99\x34' | ./hexs
4578616d706c652073747265616d3a207f9934
% ./hexs ./hexs
7f454c460101010000000000000000000200030001000000778804083400000084200000000000003400200009002800 ...

(...'s actually are not output of hexs, but I'm showing that it's too much to fit here)
